{"tid":1844203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺人保衛家園，何罪之有","createTime":"2020-01-26T14:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T14:35:55.000Z","uid":134993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7db8019bf785a08ff5d7c426da12044fe5fe05ee","tid":1844203,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"議員表示：<br />\n<br />\n他們是作為一個守衛去保衛家園，認為他們沒有做錯"},{"pid":"34604688e4c0d8e0aee16f6275744dee253ea318","tid":1844203,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"46316724dacbe4ee9a6211fa02b1548a240a24c8","tid":1844203,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我同醫護一齊罷工</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.29抗疫三罷<br />\n每日消毒手機眼鏡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7DKFeP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7DKFeP.jpg&h=b66c14c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fegggw0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffegggw0.jpg&h=356cfd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xRLkX1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxRLkX1F.jpg&h=dfb9a9db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4hvrUu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4hvrUu.jpg&h=a375b4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醫管局員工罷工陣線</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cz3Oj3C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcz3Oj3C.jpg&h=75c5a0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRMzZ3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRMzZ3D.jpg&h=6c372ba0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a9575ac574567760ad71873ea01d6e5f99241be","tid":1844203,"uid":284590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"人哋係係保家衛族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7a6dae178e61c75904aeb2ae59020020d072a1","tid":1844203,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcc16485707d7366c8f62ab8aee173a1c56fb813","tid":1844203,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}